      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">Inventories, requisitions, invoices, and other documents from the US Quartermaster's Dept.  These records were written during the Civil War and primarily consist of materials requested or released by US Army Quartermaster Perley P. Pitkin.</abstract>
